    public class QueryComponentImpl
extends PAVComponentBase<QueryComponent,QueryPlace>
implements QueryComponent
    General setup for the query component. Sets dependency injections, provides a place as the default place for the app. There is some boilerplate here that could eventually be avoided via annotations and code generation.
